# Language: English Only

- **All user-facing strings** (labels, buttons, messages, errors, toasts) must be in English.
- **Comments and documentation** in source code must be in English.
- **Script output** (echo, console.log) must be in English.
- Do not add new Turkish text. If you find Turkish, translate it to English.
